{"tid":1967743,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"由零開始教起，唔識煮飯嘅人  — 「韓式炒粉絲」","createTime":"2020-04-11T07:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T06:33:31.000Z","uid":68594,"like":63,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3304a60ddc601260fe3900b80afb4301621196","tid":1967743,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"有個朋友想學下「麵食」嘅關係，咁啱早兩日原來買咗啲粉絲返屋企未煮，所以今日晏晝就攞嚟做午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮個韓式炒粉絲<br />\n<br />\n材料<br />\n粉絲<br />\n牛肉片半磅<br />\n甘筍半個<br />\n雞蛋兩隻（整蛋皮）<br />\n青椒半個<br />\n洋蔥半個<br />\n菇<br />\n蒜蓉醬(可落可唔落)<br />\n<br />\n醬汁<br />\n240ml水<br />\n40ml豉油<br />\n糖4匙<br />\n雞粉一匙<br />\n韓式辣醬3匙(酒樓匙羹)<br />\n麻油(可落可唔落)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fn8Q3Bj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffn8Q3Bj.png&h=31b74260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n步驟<br />\n1.粉絲用暖水浸泡若8分鐘，至軟身即可<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfsqSuZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfsqSuZ.png&h=adf05571&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ndULP9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ndULP9.png&h=5cc64c43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfmfvgY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfmfvgY.png&h=bb91536c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iW8mqQr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiW8mqQr.png&h=65e34b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.將所有材料切絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8qcxw2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8qcxw2.png&h=3a9699d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhcnaiR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhcnaiR.png&h=24ed0cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awZHULE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawZHULE.png&h=42579314&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8vLSxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8vLSxu.png&h=c17ebb78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaROQjq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaROQjq.png&h=8585344e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.1 煎蛋皮，切絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J3y9zMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3y9zMt.png&h=0d76b0da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNsN5Tt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNsN5Tt.png&h=bbfe242d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdjEcyz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdjEcyz.png&h=2e10fdc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkEMB0o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkEMB0o.png&h=f4683a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.落多油大火炒香牛肉片，並可落一匙蒜蓉醬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Fdd1sq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Fdd1sq.png&h=d5777c91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w95v3FT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw95v3FT.png&h=425025aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.落菇、洋蔥、甘筍炒至軟身(約2分鐘)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0EMB09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0EMB09.png&h=4779a6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjdmqUC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjdmqUC.png&h=f3f10e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5.落青椒及粉絲炒，落醬汁(若有痴底情況可稍微熄一熄火)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVWrB1x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVWrB1x.png&h=0a2a39b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1EXJGG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1EXJGG.png&h=520b7d61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4DYs8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4DYs8v.png&h=ce1eac49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.落雞蛋絲，炒勻所有野，上碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfv75VC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcfv75VC.png&h=942fddb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5UAvnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5UAvnB.jpg&h=ef9528a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附上自製洋蔥泡菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJnqSBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJnqSBc.png&h=3b135e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9925fa189c22b6f88de10ec60d6738ad5ec54480","tid":1967743,"uid":216643,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c274e06f16a6bf7ef464b53111696536e08fd3","tid":1967743,"uid":203945,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"隻貓好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cdc8a2cf5be7f517d49395cfde8e54429b546d","tid":1967743,"uid":63303,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:17:36.000Z","msg":"貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627cfd62a44c0b849bd54ae82c151d99b4b636c6","tid":1967743,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"65c274e06f16a6bf7ef464b53111696536e08fd3","tid":1967743,"uid":203945,"